data.description: This 4 bedroom/2 bath home located in the desirable Cliffs subdivision is inviting with vaulted ceilings and open spacious kitchen and dining area. Plenty of room for everyone with a separate living and family room.  Oversized 2 car garage meets your all your storage needs. Fenced backyard and covered back patio perfect for entertaining. New water heater.  New A/C & heating system. New dishwasher.  New range/oven.  New microwave.   A new solar panel system will cover your electric bills, so the only bill you'll pay is water/trash.
data.whatILove: This home has lots of room to spread out. Easy access for those who may have disabilities with everything on one level and no steps. The master bathroom has an easily accessible shower and room for 2 to get ready at the same time. Nice laundry room with base cabinets and room for either a stackable or side by side washer and dryer and room for more shelves. The garage has attic access for more storage. Nice size living room, family room and a dining area. Kitchen has a very nice size island with base cabinets, large work surface and area for bar stools which is great for entertaining. Easy access pantry in kitchen. Kitchen has new faucet, garbage disposal, dishwasher,  glass top electric stove, and microwave. These were purchased at the end of 2017, all stainless steel and made by Whirlpool. New electric hot water heater installed spring of 2017. New heating and cooling system installed in spring of 2017. Everything is connected to the solar unit which was installed in the fall of 2017. This house is set for move in and lots of possibilities. The yard is fenced in but there is plenty of room to expand and add anything you want and the views are very nice.  The yard has 2 fruit trees and is set up on an irrigation system. It is a very quiet neighborhood with friendly neighbors! Come check it out!
